Our Fiction Buyer Makes Her Selections <http://email.bn.com/cgi-bin6/flo?y=hFVU0EUb180Bvf0FIN0Aq>	   <http://www.readersadvantage.com/newsletter/images/dot_clear.gif>	Great Reads  Exclusive <http://www.readersadvantage.com/newsletter/images/exclusive_sm.gif>
Our Fiction Buyer Makes Her Selections <http://email.bn.com/cgi-bin6/flo?y=hFVU0EUb180Bvf0FIN0Aq>
Whether it's a new collection of short stories by old favorites or a debut novel we highly recommend, February offers a wide assortment of fiction for all readers. Our Fiction buyer, Sessalee Hensley, has culled through the best of the month to select a few great new books <http://email.bn.com/cgi-bin6/flo?y=hFVU0EUb180Bvf0FIN0Aq> we think you should know about.	 
