Book Alert <http://email.bn.com/cgi-bin6/flo?y=hFVU0EUb180Bvf0FIL0Ao>	   <http://www.readersadvantage.com/newsletter/images/dot_clear.gif>	Book Alert
8 Great Titles You Can Preorder Now <http://email.bn.com/cgi-bin6/flo?y=hFVU0EUb180Bvf0FIL0Ao>
Michael J. Fox's much-awaited memoir is due April 4th, but it's not the only big book we're looking forward to in the coming months -- Fran Drescher and Bobby Knight will also be telling their stories. Plus, a new Spenser mystery from Robert B. Parker is on the way, Ian McEwan's Atonement will soon be crossing the waters, and Jean M. Auel's Shelters of Stone is less than an Ice Age away. These and more are all available for preorder now <http://email.bn.com/cgi-bin6/flo?y=hFVU0EUb180Bvf0FIL0Ao>.	 
